<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَا بَاشِقُ ارْحَمْني وَرِقَّ لحَالَتي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>دَعْني لأَفْرَاخِي الصِّغَارِ أَطِيرُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَتُصَفِّقُ الأَوْرَاقُ عِنْدَ سَمَاعِهَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>صَوْتي وَيَهْتِفُ بِالخَرِيرِ غَدِيرُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مَاذَا جَنَيْتُ وَإِنَّني يَا سَيِّدِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>طَيرٌ ضَعِيفٌ جُنحُهُ مَكْسُورُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مَا في حَيَاتي لِلرُّبى ضَرَرٌ وَلاَ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>جَوْرٌ وَيَكْفِي أَنَّني عُصْفُورُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مُتَنَقِّلٌ بَينَ الغُصُونِ كَأَنَّني<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>ظِلٌّ أَظَلُّ مَدَى النَّهَارِ أَدُورُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِنيِّ خَطِيبٌ وَالْغُصُونُ مَنَابِرِي<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَالسَّامِعُونَ جَدَاوِلٌ وَزُهُورُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">فَرَدَّ الْبَاشِقُ عَلَيْهِ قَائِلاً:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>خَلِّ الْبُكَاءَ فَلَيْسَ دَمْعُكَ مُشْبِعَاً<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>جَوْفي وَنَارُ الجُوعِ فِيهِ سَعِيرُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أَنَا إِنْ رَثِيتُ لأَنَّةٍ أَوْ زَفْرَةٍ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَيَسُدُّ جُوعِيَ أَنَّةٌ وَزَفِيرُ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أَنْتَ الْكَبِيرُ عَلَى الْبَعُوضِ تَصِيدُهُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَأَنَا عَلَى هَذَا الْكَبِيرِ كَبِيرُ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>